  const branchDismissalPeriod = 7;

  const getCookie = (name, req) => {
  if (req === null || req === void 0 ? void 0 : req.cookies) {
    return req.cookies[name];
  } else if (typeof document !== 'undefined') {
    const cookies = document.cookie.split(';'); // Iterate all cookies

    for (let i = 0; i < cookies.length; i++) {
      const cookie = cookies[i]; // Determine separator index ("name=value")

      let separatorIndex = cookie.indexOf('='); // IE<11 emits the equal sign when the cookie value is empty

      separatorIndex = separatorIndex < 0 ? cookie.length : separatorIndex;
      const cookieName = decodeURIComponent(cookie.slice(0, separatorIndex).replace(/^\s+/, '')); // Return cookie value if the name matches

      if (cookieName === name) {
        return decodeURIComponent(cookie.slice(separatorIndex + 1));
      }
    }
  }
}

  const setCookie = (name, value, res, {
  overwrite = true,
  domain = '.trulia.com',
  expires = 365,
  path = '/',
  secure,
  httponly,
  samesite
} = {}) => {
  if (res === null || res === void 0 ? void 0 : res.cookie) {
    const now = new Date();
    res.cookie(name, value, {
      overwrite,
      domain,
      expires: expires > 0 ? new Date(now.setTime(now.getTime() + expires * 86400000)) : 0,
      path,
      secure,
      httponly,
      samesite
    });
  } else if (typeof document !== 'undefined') {
    // Determine cookie expiration date
    // If succesful the result will be a valid Date, otherwise it will be an invalid Date or false(ish)
    const expDate = expires ? new Date( // in case expires is an integer, it should specify the number of days till the cookie expires
    typeof expires === 'number' ? new Date().getTime() + expires * 864e5 // else expires should be either a Date object or in a format recognized by Date.parse()
    : expires) : 0; // Set cookie

    document.cookie = name.replace(/[^+#$&^`|]/g, encodeURIComponent) // Encode cookie name
    .replace('(', '%28').replace(')', '%29') + '=' + value.replace(/[^+#$&/:<-[\]-}]/g, encodeURIComponent) // Encode cookie value (RFC6265)
    + (expDate && expDate.getTime() >= 0 ? ';expires=' + expDate.toUTCString() : '') // Add expiration date
    + (domain ? ';domain=' + domain : '') // Add domain
    + (path ? ';path=' + path : '') // Add path
    + (secure ? ';secure' : '') // Add secure option
    + (httponly ? ';httponly' : '') // Add httponly option
    + (samesite ? ';samesite=' + samesite : ''); // Add samesite option
  }
}

  const deleteCookie = (name, options) => {
  return setCookie(name, '', undefined, {
    expires: -1,
    domain: options && options.domain,
    path: options && options.path,
    secure: 0,
    httponly: 0
  });
}

  function removeBranchBannerBodyClassName() {
  if (document.body.className && document.body.className.includes('branch-banner-is-active')) {
    document.body.className = document.body.className.replace('branch-banner-is-active', '');
  }
}

  function removeBodyStyle() {
  document.body.removeAttribute('style');
}

  function setBranchBannerBodyClassName() {
  if (!document.body.className.includes('branch-banner-is-active')) {
    document.body.className += ' branch-banner-is-active';
  }
}

  const didCloseHandler = function didCloseHandler() {
  if (typeof document === 'undefined' || !document.body) {
    return;
  }

  setCookie('branch_banner_closed', 'true', undefined, {
    expires: branchDismissalPeriod
  });
  removeBranchBannerBodyClassName();
  removeBodyStyle();
  removeAllHandlers();
}
  const willNotShowHandler = function willNotShowHandler() {
  if (typeof document === 'undefined' || !document.body) {
    return;
  }

  const cookieVal = getCookie('branch_banner_closed');

  if (!cookieVal || cookieVal === 'false') {
    setCookie('branch_banner_closed', 'true', undefined, {
      expires: branchDismissalPeriod
    });
  }

  removeBranchBannerBodyClassName();
  removeBodyStyle();
  removeAllHandlers();
}
  const willShowHandler = function willShowHandler() {
  if (typeof document === 'undefined' || !document.body) {
    return;
  }

  const cookieVal = getCookie('branch_banner_closed');

  if (cookieVal === 'true') {
    deleteCookie('branch_banner_closed', undefined, {
      domain: '.trulia.com',
      path: '/'
    });
  }
}

  function removeAllHandlers() {
  branch.removeListener(didCloseHandler);
  branch.removeListener(willNotShowHandler);
  branch.removeListener(willShowHandler);
}

  branch.addListener('willNotShowJourney', willNotShowHandler);
  branch.addListener('willShowJourney', willShowHandler);
  branch.addListener('didCloseJourney', didCloseHandler);

        adBlockerDetectionTimeout = setTimeout(function() {
          if (!didBranchScriptRun && typeof removeBranchBannerBodyClassName === 'function'
            && typeof removeBodyStyle === 'function' && typeof setCookie === 'function'
          ) {
            removeBranchBannerBodyClassName();
            removeBodyStyle();
            setCookie('branch_banner_closed', 'true', undefined, {
              expires: 14,
            });
          }
        }, 15000);

          function initTracking(pageviewPayload) {
    let count = 0;
    const MAX_COUNT = 100;
    window.s = window.s || {};
    window.trulia = window.trulia || {};
    window.trulia.dataLayer = window.trulia.dataLayer || {};
    window.trulia.dataLayer.referrer = document.referrer;

    function listenersDefined() {
      const listeners = window.trulia.dataLayer.listeners;
      return typeof listeners !== 'undefined' && listeners.length !== 0;
    }

    const queue = [];

    const track = function (event, data, isInitialPageView) {
      if (processQueue()) {
        handleEvent(event, data, isInitialPageView);
      } else {
        queue.push({
          event: event,
          data: data,
          isInitialPageView: isInitialPageView
        });
      }
    };

    const handleEvent = function (event, data, isInitialPageView) {
      if (isInitialPageView) {
        window.s.referrer = window.trulia.dataLayer.referrer;
      }

      trulia.dataLayer.listeners.forEach(function (listener) {
        listener(event, data);
      });
    };

    const processQueue = function () {
      if (listenersDefined()) {
        if (queue.length) {
          let queuedData;

          while (queuedData = queue.shift()) {
            handleEvent(queuedData.event, queuedData.data, queuedData.isInitialPageView);
          }
        }

        return true;
      }

      if (count <= MAX_COUNT) {
        setTimeout(processQueue, 300);
        count += 1;
      }

      return false;
    };

    if (pageviewPayload) {
      track('trackState', pageviewPayload, true);
    }

    window.trulia.dataLayer.track = track;
  }
